claim.claim-text:
6. An ultrasonic imaging apparatus for scanning a measurement target in an object to be inspected by using ultrasonic beams and receiving echoes of the ultrasonic beams reflected by the measurement target to obtain image data on the measurement target, said apparatus comprising: 
transmission side signal processing means for providing drive signals; 
an ultrasonic probe for transmitting ultrasonic beams by using a plurality of ultrasonic transducer elements in accordance with the drive signals provided by said transmission side signal processing means and detecting echoes of the transmitted ultrasonic beams to obtain detection signals; 
reception side signal processing means for amplifying the detection signals output from said ultrasonic probe and obtaining image data on the measurement target on the basis of the amplified detection signals; and 
control means for controlling said transmission side signal processing means to transmit ultrasonic beams simultaneously in a plurality of directions toward the measurement target from said plurality of ultrasonic transducer elements and controlling said reception side signal processing means to process the detection signals obtained by said ultrasonic probe and form a plurality of receiving focal points with respect to each of the transmitted ultrasonic beams.
